&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    曹源池庭園の別の写真を共有します。バックグラウンドは嵐山です。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Gardens" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">I had to share another shot of Sogenchi Garden, with Mt. Arashi in the background.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2011_A7R00279.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Changing Colors at Tenryu-ji・紅葉の天龍寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201101/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Changing Colors at Tenryu-ji・紅葉の天龍寺" /><published>2020-11-01T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-11-01T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sogenchi</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201101/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
