    天龍寺の庭も色付いています。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">View of the Sogenchi Garden at Tenryu-ji Temple this morning.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2011_A7R00272.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Autumn Leaves・紅葉</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201031/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Autumn Leaves・紅葉" /><published>2020-10-31T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-31T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/colored-leaves</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201031/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Autumn leaves against a blue sky.
&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    青い空を背景に紅葉。      
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html">Autumn leaves against a blue sky.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2020/2010_A7R00254.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">River at Dawn・夜明けの川</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201029/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="River at Dawn・夜明けの川" /><published>2020-10-29T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2020-10-29T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/river-at-dawn</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/201029/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
